{"tid":1698031,"cid":31,"subCid":9,"title":"仲有無人訂光復香港旗","createTime":"2019-11-07T08:32:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-16T13:17:08.000Z","uid":241955,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"988fe429fd42b468d29945a182465ece48cdcb92","tid":1698031,"uid":241955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T08:32:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tgVXZQ1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtgVXZQ1.jpg&h=46be875a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PQgfDL7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPQgfDL7.jpg&h=62fd45e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/S57Oejt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FS57Oejt.jpg&h=e71a6d64&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Pk4H29q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPk4H29q.jpg&h=6e455aeb&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n之前成日有人問有無英文<br />\n咁終於就整左支英文版<br />\n英文支旗個設計其實都係一支旗嚟,個感嘆號係旗桿<br />\n黑色中文,本民前藍都係繼續會有既<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cuhkantielab/videos/440551836594232?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcuhkantielab%2Fvideos%2F440551836594232%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=Z9XWEpuBYzNDjlwSEAyqK2lERb1kSGFVDbesiz0gOXg%3D&h=86c23235\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cuhkantielab/videos/440551836594232?sfns=mo</a><br />\n暴大升咗我地支旗,好感動<br />\n其實一齊訂旗就係想大家可以周圍都舉<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZUGEifz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZUGEifz.jpg&h=68d890a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vjdSjpt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvjdSjpt.jpg&h=a7cbd407&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SAUumCV.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSAUumCV.gif&h=7cff0a16&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n旗就230$一支台灣飛香港(非現貨)<br />\ne家訂估計大概11月2x號會有(11號截單)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EgUEFDK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEgUEFDK.jpg&h=84ce92a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/faNF9xn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfaNF9xn.jpg&h=0f97be68&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RGvAdY3.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRGvAdY3.gif&h=ebf948d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n請join channel 聯絡<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/AAAAAEvMDY0LDpjiKNkstA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FAAAAAEvMDY0LDpjiKNkstA&d=Z9XWEpuBYzNDjlwSEAyqK2lERb1kSGFVDbesiz0gOXg%3D&h=347fe156\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/AAAAAEvMDY0LDpjiKNkstA</a>"},{"pid":"e990ab1fecdd48b06d5f612fb24319cf0b083b74","tid":1698031,"uid":165840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T08:37:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e59f6b93ffb7f67385dd79ddf45bb1c0a6990a9a","tid":1698031,"uid":78349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T08:42:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O5v5PB1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO5v5PB1.png&h=b7059c9d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n幫推呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6efd6ae16c37fb6b8cd14f31152ff4487dceac69","tid":1698031,"uid":195812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T16:33:08.000Z","msg":"有冇現貨"},{"pid":"078e5f015c666e5d7c38970e17